(firstQuint)Epidemiology of Conjunctivitis in the Emergency Department.

 The purpose of this study was to determine the epidemiology of ocular emergencies in a Reference Ophthalmological Hospital in Goiania, with emphasis on acute infectious conjunctivitis, morbidity with a higher incidence in this Service.

 It aims to delineate the main etiologies found among infectious conjunctivitis and to compare them with those found in several other reference services in Ophthalmology.

